{"tid":269252,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"遊玩時 開心一點 不必掛念我","createTime":"2017-06-03T15:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T15:54:04.000Z","uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ca0f465c0df197dfbfc4549486fa20e72a17a2","tid":269252,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&amp;v=HheRowgf6rk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dplayer_embedded%26v%3DHheRowgf6rk&d=LFPffSP%2B5dJGqMzEehvWeTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2dcfb4c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&amp;v=HheRowgf6rk</a> <br />\n<br />\n遊玩時 開心一點 不必掛念我 <br />\n來好好給我活著 就似最初 <br />\n仍然在呼吸都應該 要慶賀 <br />\n如果想哭 可試試對嘉賓滿座 <br />\n說個笑話 紀念我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7904dd93f5b1b1ccbdf049d6dfdb6cc48aea783","tid":269252,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:37:40.000Z","msg":"放心 冇人會"},{"pid":"5b057688a266a161940c3b97b15cf16e7d6a7b9d","tid":269252,"uid":76420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放心 冇人會</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6409496bb2998e7e099982604dc834804eef3cf","tid":269252,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"無人會 放心"},{"pid":"cb04b9a687ef3bb07b1c3488ebc3d3e1a0832a15","tid":269252,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人會 放心</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}